These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, lemon, cabbage, corn
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, chinchilla, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, bike, train
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person driving the train is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the bike and the person eating lemon##2
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | cabbage | corn  | lemon | cucumber  |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog  | guinea-pig       | chinchilla     |
| Transport   | bike     | car | train       | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, sudoku, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, crime, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, badminton, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | board-games | video-games    | traveling  | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | time-travel  | spy   | crime    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | skiing | badminton      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, water, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving, dancing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, disco, r&b
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | juice         | almond-milk   | water    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | woodworking | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | hip-hop        | r&b      | trance   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, italian, turkish, canadian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, soccer, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the van and the canadian##2
3. the turkish is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the russian##1
6. the person driving the van is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian        | italian   | russian | turkish |
| Sport         | soccer | sailing | snowboarding    | ice-hockey |
| Transport     | trike       | skateboard     | van       | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, sprite, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, reading, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, swimming, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is video-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | soy-milk      | water       | sprite   |
| Hobby      | video-games   | rock-climbing  | fishing | reading     |
| Sport      | skateboarding     | biathlon | swimming        | climbing |

