.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, corn, strawberry, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, singing, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting, handball, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person eating corn##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's sport is handball##2
6. the person eating corn is between the person eating apricot and the person eating strawberry##2
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry | corn  | apricot | radish      |
| Hobby   | singing  | chess  | dancing | filmmaking |
| Sport   | parkour | water-polo | weightlifting | handball     |

