.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, pumpkin, grapes, nectarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, sports, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person eating pumpkin is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching sports movies##2
7. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | grapes  | pumpkin    | nectarine | cucumber  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster       | romance        | adventure    |
| Sport         | basketball | soccer | tennis  | swimming |

