.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, fishing, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, romance, documentary
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, guinea-pig, fish
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the fish and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | puzzles  | dancing | fishing | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | documentary | satire   | romance         |
| Pet           | frog | guinea-pig  | hedgehog   | fish      |

