.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, plum, apricot, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, skydiving, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, funk, gospel, jazz
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the person eating plum##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple  | avocado    | apricot | plum       |
| Hobby         | reading | drawing | filmmaking  | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | jazz      | funk  | pop     |

