.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, nectarine, cauliflower, pineapple
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, skydiving, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, drama, superhero
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
3. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating broccoli and the person who's hobby is chess##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
8. the person watching horror movies is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cauliflower      | pineapple | nectarine | broccoli |
| Hobby         | fishing   | chess  | camping | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | horror   | documentary | drama |

