.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, peach, radish, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing, woodworking, card-games
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, bird, snake
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person eating peach##1
3. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the owner of the mouse and the person eating cauliflower##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the snake##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | cauliflower  | radish | pumpkin | peach     |
| Hobby   | sudoku | woodworking   | card-games  | fishing    |
| Pet     | ferret        | snake       | mouse      | bird |

