The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, baking, filmmaking, video-games
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, lizard, hamster
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking water is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is baking##2
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk     | water | soy-milk       |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | video-games | collecting  | baking |
| Pet        | hamster  | hedgehog      | lizard        | goldfish      |

