.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, police-officer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, family, western, action
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the coach##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person watching western movies and the security-guard##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the roller is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | dressmaker | police-officer | security-guard    | coach   |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | family   | action | comedy |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | roller       | snowmobile        | helicopter    |

