There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, tea, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, metal, pop, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, russian, indonesian
1. the fan of gospel is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking tea and the colombian##2
3. the person drinking tea is the fan of metal##1
4. the person drinking tea is between the fan of pop and the indonesian##2
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the nigerian is between the russian and the fan of classical##2
7. the fan of gospel is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | sprite | tea | water   | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | metal    | pop   | classical     |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | russian | nigerian | colombian   |

