There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, lemonade, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: tomato, raspberry, plum, cabbage
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, tennis, badminton
1. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
2. the person eating plum is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is tennis##2
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating plum##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | juice | iced-tea           | lemonade |
| Food       | tomato | plum    | raspberry          | cabbage   |
| Sport      | tennis  | lacrosse   | badminton | skiing  |

