The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, adventure, martial-arts, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, frog, goldfish
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking 7up is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking lemonade and the owner of the ferret##2
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | 7up | lemonade     | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | time-travel        | martial-arts  | adventure  |
| Pet           | ferret      | goldfish         | bird | frog |

