3. the lawyer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the electrician##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | lawyer        | electrician  | chef | bartender   |
| Sport       | biathlon | rowing | skateboarding    | badminton |
| Transport   | trike        | motorbike     | airplane       | van      |

