.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, kale, cherry, peas
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, dog, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, van, quad-bike, bike
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person eating peas and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | peas | kale | pomegranate | cherry |
| Pet         | chinchilla       | goldfish     | dog   | frog   |
| Transport   | ship | van | quad-bike | bike |

 